Get in touch with us here at %%site.name%%, we really want to hear your feedback.

Email
-----

The best way to reach us is by sending an email to [%%site.email%%](mailto:%%site.email%%).

Post a notice
-------------

If you have a question about how to do something, you can post a public message 
by using @public in the message body. Watch the [public timeline](%%action.public%%) for answers; 
they'll usually start with "@" plus your user name.

Bugs
----

If you think you've found a bug in %%site.name%% please report it! We are still in beta and welcome any 
and all problems you have with the site, just email: [bugs@centralflirt.com](mailto:bugs@centralflirt.com).